<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Chat Admin — <%= user %></title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/portfolio.css">
</head>
<body class="admin-page">

<header class="admin-header">
  <h1>Chat Admin — <%= user %></h1>
  <nav style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center;">
    <a href="/admin">Projects</a>
    <a href="/admin/models">Models</a>
    <a href="/admin/chatlogs">Chat logs</a>
    <form method="POST" action="/admin/logout"><button type="submit">Sign out</button></form>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="admin-section">
  <h2>Projects</h2>
  <p>Projects store chat memory. When a user types <code>/slug</code> at the start or end of a message, that exchange is tagged to the project.</p>
  <table class="admin-table">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Name</th><th>Slug</th><th>Depth</th><th>Memories</th><th>Last activity</th><th>CV</th><th></th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <% for (const p of projects) { %>
    <tr>
      <td><a href="/admin/projects/<%= p.slug %>"><%= p.name %></a></td>
      <td style="font-family:var(--mono);">/<%= p.slug %></td>
      <td><%= p.context_depth %></td>
      <td><%= p.memory_count %></td>
      <td><%= p.last_activity ? new Date(p.last_activity * 1000).toISOString().slice(0,16).replace('T',' ') : '–' %></td>
      <td><%= p.is_cv_context ? '✓' : '–' %></td>
      <td>
        <details>
          <summary>Edit</summary>
          <form method="POST" action="/admin/projects/<%= p.id %>" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-top:6px;">
            <input name="name" value="<%= p.name %>" required>
            <input name="slug" value="<%= p.slug %>" required>
            <input name="context_depth" type="number" value="<%= p.context_depth %>" style="width:70px">
            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;"><input type="checkbox" name="is_cv_context" value="1" <%= p.is_cv_context ? 'checked' : '' %>> CV</label>
            <button type="submit">Save</button>
          </form>
          <form method="POST" action="/admin/projects/<%= p.id %>/delete" style="margin-top:6px;" onsubmit="return confirm('Delete project <%= p.slug %> and its memories?')">
            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;"><input type="checkbox" name="keep_messages" value="1"> Keep messages (untag)</label>
            <button type="submit">Delete</button>
          </form>
        </details>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <% } %>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <details class="add-form">
    <summary>Add project</summary>
    <form method="POST" action="/admin/projects">
      <input name="name" placeholder="Name (e.g. Beacon)" required>
      <input name="slug" placeholder="slug (e.g. beacon)" required pattern="[a-z0-9-]+">
      <input name="context_depth" type="number" placeholder="Context depth" value="20">
      <label><input type="checkbox" name="is_cv_context" value="1"> Include in CV context</label>
      <button type="submit">Add</button>
    </form>
  </details>
</section>

<section class="admin-section">
  <h2>MCP endpoints</h2>
  <p>For a future MCP server to read this project memory. Send <code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;</code> (set <code><%= user === 'douglas' ? 'DCHAT_MCP_TOKEN' : 'NCHAT_MCP_TOKEN' %></code> in the server <code>.env</code>).</p>
  <ul style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;">
    <li>GET <code>/mcp/projects</code> — list projects with memory counts</li>
    <li>GET <code>/mcp/projects/:slug</code> — fetch memories (query: <code>?since=unix_ts&amp;limit=500</code>)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

</body>
</html>
